<HEADLINE>
<P>
EX-JOINT CHIEFS ON GULF CRISIS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Oh, that we had elected a facsimile of Harry Truman! He wasn't about to let 
countless American youths be slaughtered invading an alien land, not when he 
