<P>
LOS ANGELES DODGERS (BASEBALL TEAM); VALENZUELA, FERNANDO; HATCHER, MICKEY; 
SAMUEL, JUAN; ARBITRATION; BASEBALL PLAYERS -- CONTRACTS 
</P>
