chairman during the past three years. Chambers, president and chief executive 
of Chambers Communications Corp. of Eugene, Ore., served three years as a 
director of the Portland branch beginning in 1980, joined the San Francisco 
board in 1985 and has been its deputy chairman since 1988. Times Mirror owns 
the Los Angeles Times and other media properties. 
